text.section:
The Department of Parks shall establish a steering committee which shall consist of:
The secretary of the Finance and Administration Cabinet, or a designee;
The Commissioner of Agriculture, or a designee;
The commissioner of the Department of Parks, or a designee;
The director of the Agriculture Development Board, or a designee;
The coordinator of the Kentucky State University Aquaculture Program, or a designee;
The chairperson of the horticulture department at the University of Kentucky, or a designee; and
Two (2) members of organizations and associations representing the Kentucky farming community, appointed by the Commissioner of Agriculture.
